S.FORM: alang Gukut ga niya mki sku Karing Keng atu Syurin go, kwara sali buwan nya ga 174 buwan, 543 hi ku kwara s'uli tayan. s'uli tayan pinspngan Gyencumin ga 94% kyan ku 508 hi, binah ga, 'yat kahun sku pinspngan Gyencumin ga 6% kyan ku 35 hi nya. pinspung na linhuyan Gyencumin ga, Truku 83%, Amis 3%, Tayan 4%, Paywan 2%, binah lihuyan s'uli 3%. maki qu ngasal bziran. rhzyal kki'an tay 'llaw na Gukut hya' ga bsilung. tay 'zil na Gukut hya' ga rgyax krahu'. tay mkyahu' na Gukut hya' ga bsilung. tay mkraya' na Gukut hya' ga rgyax krahu'. tay mkraya' na Gukut hya' ga Knlibu. tay mkyahu' na Gukut hya' ga Qnragan. rekisi kayal kyokay maki 1 kyokay. ssquliq pinlpgan ppqbaqan pqwasan biru 'laqi' cikuy pqwasan biru 'laqi' mrkyas tuqi 'san basu kisya' glgan spyangan na pinbahu Ubuy qqmayh

alang Gokot ga niya mki sko Karing Keng ato Syorin go, kwara sali bowan nya ga 174 bowan, 543 hi ko kwara s'oli tayan. s'oli tayan pinspngan Gyencomin ga 94% kyan ko 508 hi, binah ga, 'yat kahon sko pinspngan Gyencomin ga 6% kyan ko 35 hi nya. pinspong na linhoyan Gyencomin ga, Troko 83%, Amis 3%, Tayan 4%, Paywan 2%, binah lihoyan s'oli 3%. maki qo ngasal bziran. rhzyal kki'an tay 'llaw na Gokot hya' ga bsilong. tay 'zil na Gokot hya' ga rgyax kraho'. tay mkyaho' na Gokot hya' ga bsilong. tay mkraya' na Gokot hya' ga rgyax kraho'. tay mkraya' na Gokot hya' ga Knlibo. tay mkyaho' na Gokot hya' ga Qnragan. rekisi kayal kyokay maki 1 kyokay. ssqoliq pinlpgan ppqbaqan pqwasan biro 'laqi' cikoy pqwasan biro 'laqi' mrkyas toqi 'san baso kisya' glgan spyangan na pinbaho Uboy qqmayh
